        "# 🎬 Task 1: Production-Grade Data Cleaning & Preprocessing Pipeline\n",
        "### **Project**: Netflix Movies and TV Shows Analysis\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 📌 1. Project Overview & Objectives\n",
        "Data preprocessing is the most critical foundation of any analytics or machine learning lifecycle. Raw data collected from production systems is often riddled with missing values, structural irregularities, structural duplicates, and incorrect type inferences.\n",
        "\n",
        "### 🎯 Key Objectives:\n",
        "* Implement a repeatable and robust data-cleaning pipeline using Python (`Pandas`).\n",
        "* Identify, quantify, and treat systemic missing data ($NaN$s) and duplicate records.\n",
        "* Enforce structural and semantic consistency across textual features and date signatures.\n",
        "* Validate data schema integrity to guarantee downstream readiness for Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) and Modeling."
      ],
