    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 👥 6. Identical Row / Duplicate Record Diagnostics\n",
        "Duplicate rows can artificially skew downstream analysis. We perform a key-space diagnostic sweep to detect and remove identical records or ID overlaps."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "JiPYMm6R2BXB"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# ==========================================\n",
        "# CELL 12: DUPLICATE DETECTION SWEEP\n",
        "# Why: Verify the uniqueness of primary entity identifiers (`show_id`).\n",
        "# ==========================================\n",
        "\n",
        "total_duplicates = df.duplicated().sum()\n",
        "id_duplicates = df.duplicated(subset=['show_id']).sum()\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"=== EVALUATION OF DUPLICATE ENTITY LATTICES ===\")\n",
        "print(f\"Complete system identical rows detected: {total_duplicates}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Primary Key Constraints Broken ('show_id' duplicates): {id_duplicates}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "if total_duplicates > 0:\n",
        "    df.drop_duplicates(inplace=True)\n",
        "    print(\"[ACTION] Dropped structural duplicates from processing matrix.\")\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print(\"[STATUS] No structural integrity duplication found.\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "ieDjeKTX2Dib",
        "outputId": "5a219d2e-f2e6-4f68-fbf9-150d065f09eb"
